column2: SELECT   s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, s.z, p.ra, p.dec, s.zwarning,   g.h_delta_eqw, g.h_delta_eqw_err,   g.h_alpha_eqw, g.h_alpha_eqw_err  FROM GalSpecLine AS g  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid  JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE  g.h_delta_eqw > #   AND g.h_alpha_eqw < # AND s.class = &&&  AND s.zwarning = #
